steps.name: "Find Shipment" window opens and click Add button
Click ellipsis button next to "Ship To" button and "Find Facility Address" window opens
Enter "My First Customer" and click Find button and click OK button
Click Yes on the Attention window
Enter Shipment name and enter Location
Enter Notes and enter Additional_Info and enter Issued_By
Click Shipping_Items tab and click Add_Asset button
Enter "Sample-10" and then click Find button
Double-click search result and click OK button
Click Add_Non_Asset button and "Add Shipment Item" window is open
Click Save button and then click Close button
Enter search value for the Shipment Name and click Find button
Click OK button and "Edit Shipment" window opens
